Release Stable version v0.7.2 · koalaman/shellcheck · GitHub
bash - How to install shellcheck 0.7.0 version in Ubuntu 18.04 - Ask Ubuntu

	Ø Install ShellCheck
	
sudo su -
wget https://github.com/koalaman/shellcheck/releases/download/v0.7.2/shellcheck-v0.7.2.linux.x86_64.tar.xz
tar -xvf shellcheck-v0.7.2.linux.x86_64.tar.xz
cd shellcheck-v0.7.2
cp shellcheck /usr/local/bin


	Ø Check ShellCheck version
	
shellcheck --version
ShellCheck - shell script analysis tool
version: 0.7.0
license: GNU General Public License, version 3
website: https://www.shellcheck.net
